{"tid":885353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要將人分類分等級","createTime":"2018-11-01T09:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T09:28:40.000Z","uid":207799,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3174190df4bdbdb00be459faed02d3cb6695d85","tid":885353,"uid":207799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"啲人天生樣衰 或者膚色唔同 佢地都唔想<br />\n由細細個幼稚園已經開始因為樣衰俾人排擠 冇人肯同自己挽<br />\n慢慢大個就連街都唔肯出 怕人笑自己 對自己評頭品足<br />\n不過事實上就算再識打扮 有幾識襯衫著 去到尾又會衰喺個樣度<br />\n身邊既朋友全部都同自己一樣<br />\n樣衰 性格摺 冇自信<br />\n雖然佢地自己都有問題 但係多多少少都多得成長過程中啲人笑鳩佢地排擠佢地 <br />\n令佢地變到更自卑 唔識同人相處<br />\n包容多啲啦 香港人 有頭髮邊個想做癩痢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2bda8ceb64de96de18d8d362de97442ae8e459","tid":885353,"uid":156471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:13:31.000Z","msg":"咁如果有機會俾你揀同靚女做friend 或者同暗瘡肥婆做friend 你會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac60075373f66732be173ea42dc42a071d1e9ec7","tid":885353,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:15:11.000Z","msg":"非指樓主：<br />\n我諗我都識分，你唔係衰人，就係一條懞撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e977df5bd8ecbb19eca8342edbdb8bcf42b50635","tid":885353,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"因為人類對完美有追求"},{"pid":"e3d1e149921178872630a4cfb21c156423c8e7d0","tid":885353,"uid":52942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"見到個挽字，就知有d人比人欺凌係恰如其分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n挽你老母"},{"pid":"df8c247f33417022742c46db90dbe62b339dd131","tid":885353,"uid":114275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"挽挽挽 字都唔識打 抵你仆街"},{"pid":"2e32a0519caf26154aaf10d05569c9c4c78bfd01","tid":8